<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Anas Mansuri - Projects</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="index.html" id="branding" class="logo">Anas Mansuri</a>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="projects.html" class="current">Projects</a></li>
                    <li><a href="skills.html">Skills</a></li>
                    <li><a href="experience.html">Experience</a></li>
                    <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="projects">
            <h1>My Projects</h1>
            <div id="projects-grid">
                <!-- Project items will be loaded here by JavaScript -->
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3 class="project-title">QuickTrade Marketplace</h3>
                    <p class="project-description">An OLX-like marketplace where users can buy and sell products. Features include user authentication, product search and filters, a chat system, advertisement auto-expiry, profile management, and ad editing. It also has a custom admin panel and a fully mobile-responsive design.</p>
                    <p class="project-technologies"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Python, Django, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, SQL</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/AnasMansuri8/QuickTrade" target="_blank" class="cta-button">GitHub</a>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3 class="project-title">MobHub - Mobile Phone Store</h3>
                    <p class="project-description">An e-commerce platform for purchasing mobile phones. Features include product listing, category-based browsing, and user authentication.</p>
                    <p class="project-technologies"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Python, Django, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, SQL</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/AnasMansuri8/MobHub-ECommerce" target="_blank" class="cta-button">GitHub</a>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3 class="project-title">Wrist Gem - Watch Selling Website</h3>
                    <p class="project-description">An online watch store with a login/logout and checkout system. Includes an admin-side product and order management interface.</p>
                    <p class="project-technologies"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Laravel, PHP, SQL, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/AnasMansuri8/WristGem" target="_blank" class="cta-button">GitHub</a>
                </div>
                 <div class="project-card">
                    <h3 class="project-title">Save for Later - Bookmark Android App</h3>
                    <p class="project-description">An Android app to save and manage bookmarks. It automatically identifies tags from pasted links and categorizes bookmarks intelligently for better organization.</p>
                    <p class="project-technologies"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Android Studio, Kotlin, Firebase</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/AnasMansuri8/Save-for-Later" target="_blank" class="cta-button">GitHub</a>
                </div>
                 <div class="project-card">
                    <h3 class="project-title">Automation Projects</h3>
                    <p class="project-description">Developed an n8n automation that analyzes job posts received on Telegram and automatically applies for jobs via email or WhatsApp. Also developed an automation to manage GitHub repositories by committing a small daily task automatically to maintain consistency.</p>
                    <p class="project-technologies"><strong>Technologies:</strong> n8n, Python, Git, GitHub APIs, Telegram API</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/AnasMansuri8" target="_blank" class="cta-button">GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Anas Mansuri. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
